trans-unit.source: The type of objects in the list.
trans-unit.target: 清單中的物件型別。

trans-unit.source: <c>C</c> must implement the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract" /> interface.
trans-unit.target: <c>C</c>必須實作<see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract" />介面。

trans-unit.source: Represents a generic collection of <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract" /> objects that can be individually accessed by index.
trans-unit.target: 表示可以個別由索引存取之 <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract" /> 物件的泛型集合。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the element to get.
trans-unit.target: 要取得之項目的以零為起始的索引。

trans-unit.source: Returns the element at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 傳回位於指定之索引處的元素。

trans-unit.source: The element at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 在指定索引上的項目。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601.GetItem%2A> method does not remove the element at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601.GetItem%2A>方法不會移除指定索引處的項目。

trans-unit.source: To remove an element from the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601>, use the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601.RemoveAt%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 若要移除的項目從<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601>，使用<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601.RemoveAt%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is less than zero.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> 小於零。

trans-unit.source: -or-
<paramref name="index" /> is equal to or greater than the return value of <see cref="M:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1.GetCount" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> 等於或大於 <see cref="M:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1.GetCount" /> 的傳回值。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract" /> to locate in the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 要在 <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract`1" /> 中尋找的 <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract" />。

trans-unit.source: Returns the index of a specific element in the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 傳回 <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract`1" /> 中特定項目的索引。

trans-unit.source: The index of <paramref name="item" /> if found in the list; otherwise, -1.
trans-unit.target: 如果可在清單中找到則為 <paramref name="item" /> 的索引，否則為 -1。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index at which to insert <c>item</c>.
trans-unit.target: 要插入<c>項目</c>的索引位置 (以零為基礎)。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract" /> to insert in the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 要插入至 <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract" /> 的 <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract`1" />。

trans-unit.source: Inserts an element in the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract`1" /> at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 將項目插入 <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract`1" /> 中指定的索引處。

trans-unit.source: After you call <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601.Insert%2A>, the elements that follow the insertion point move to accommodate the new element.
trans-unit.target: 在您呼叫後<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601.Insert%2A>，元素，後面接著插入點移動以容納新項目。

trans-unit.source: The indexes of the elements that are moved are also updated.
trans-unit.target: 移動之項目的索引也會更新。

trans-unit.source: To replace an element at a specified index, use the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601.SetItem%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 若要取代指定索引處的項目，請使用<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601.SetItem%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: To determine whether an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601> is read-only, call the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract%601.GetIsReadOnly%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 若要判斷是否<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601>是唯讀的呼叫<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract%601.GetIsReadOnly%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is less than zero.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> 小於零。

trans-unit.source: -or-
<paramref name="index" /> is equal to or greater than the return value of <see cref="M:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1.GetCount" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> 等於或大於 <see cref="M:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1.GetCount" /> 的傳回值。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract`1" /> is read-only.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract`1" /> 是唯讀的。

trans-unit.source: The index of the element to remove.
trans-unit.target: 要移除的項目索引。

trans-unit.source: Removes the element at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 移除指定索引中的項目。

trans-unit.source: After you call <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601.RemoveAt%2A>, the elements that follow the removed element move to occupy the vacated spot.
trans-unit.target: 在您呼叫後<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601.RemoveAt%2A>，移除項的項目移動以佔用空出的位置。

trans-unit.source: The indexes of the elements that are moved are also updated.
trans-unit.target: 移動之項目的索引也會更新。

trans-unit.source: To determine whether an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601> is read-only, call the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract%601.GetIsReadOnly%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 若要判斷是否<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601>是唯讀的呼叫<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract%601.GetIsReadOnly%2A>方法。

trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> 等於或大於 <see cref="M:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1.GetCount" /> 的傳回值。

trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract`1" /> 是唯讀的。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index at which to set the element.
trans-unit.target: 要在其中設定項目的索引 (以零起始)。

trans-unit.source: The element to set at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 在指定之索引處要設定的項目。

trans-unit.source: Replaces the element at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 取代指定之索引處的項目。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601.SetItem%2A> method replaces the element at the specified index.

trans-unit.source: To add an element to the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601>, use the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601.Insert%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 若要加入項目加入<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601>，使用<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601.Insert%2A>方法。
